I have to admit, I really like the idea of directly switching to Boost 1.50 and use that.

@laanwj Did you yet report that Boost 1.51 bug to the Boost devs? Would be nice to notify them.
Just for comparison, my Boost command-line to build contains `--build-type=minimal stage link=static runtime-link=static threading=multi variant=release -a -j 4 --with-filesystem --with-program_options --with-system --with-thread`
